<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
		<title>Quizer - About</title>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
		<link href="../docs/theme.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
		<style>
		body {
			background: var(--bg);
			color: var(--text);
			font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
			height: 100vh;
			display: flex;
			justify-content: center;
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}

		/* Page */
		.page {
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 560px;
		}

		/* Top Bar */
		.header {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 10px;
			max-width: 560px;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.header-title {
			font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
			font-size: 1.15rem;
			font-weight: var(--weight-heavy);
		}

		.back-btn {
			width: 36px;
			height: 36px;
			border-radius: var(--card-r);
			background-color: var(--card);
			border: 1px solid var(--border);
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			cursor: pointer;
			text-decoration: none;
			transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, border 0.15s;
			flex-shrink: 0;
		}
		.back-btn:hover { background: var(--card-hover); border-color: var(--border-h); }
		.back-btn svg {
			width: 18px; height: 18px;
			stroke: var(--text); fill: none;
			stroke-width: 2px; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round;
		}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
        <div class="page">
            <div class="header">
				<a href="/" class="back-btn">
				  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
				</a>
                <span class="header-title">About</span>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 8ch;">
				<h3>Introdution</h3>
                <p>
                    This web app was made to help people post quizes rapidly,
                    and let other students attend, participate, and view their grades.
                </p>
                <p>
					Web app was made with love by students at <i>Cairo University</i>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
